ent-RMCWindowPrison-name = window
ent-RMCWindowPrison-desc = A glass window. It looks thin and flimsy. A few knocks with anything should shatter it.
ent-RMCWindowPrisonCell-name = cell window
ent-RMCWindowPrisonCell-desc = A glass window with a special rod matrix inside a wall frame.
ent-RMCWindowPrisonReinforced-name = reinforced window
ent-RMCWindowPrisonReinforced-desc = A glass window with a special rod matrix inside a wall frame. It looks rather strong. Might take a few good hits to shatter it.
ent-RMCWindowPrisonHull-name = hull window
ent-RMCWindowPrisonHull-desc = A glass window with a special rod matrix inside a wall frame. This one has an automatic shutter system to prevent any atmospheric breach.
